  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Dei Cappuccini Restaurant</strong> has a fantastic menu of typical Mediterranean dishes with a contemporary twist, which can be enjoyed in the elegant dining room or on the terrace – both have beautiful views over Amalfi.</p>
<p><strong>La Locanda Restaurant</strong> has a lovely location next to the infinity pool, surrounded by the Mediterranean garden and lemon trees. Head here for a casual lunch on the terrace that overlooks the sea.</p>
<p><strong>Dei Cappuccini Bar</strong> has a wide selection of cocktails, wines and soft drinks that can be enjoyed in the relaxed atmosphere.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools</strong></span></p>
<p>A small infinity pool provides a peaceful spot for some sunbathing and its position on the edge of the hotel’s terrace means that it boasts incredible panoramic sea views. It’s normally open from June to September.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel’s cosy wellness area features a Turkish bath, a fitness area and offers a range of massages and treatments (payable locally)</p>]]></facilityDescription>
