  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Sea View Rooms</strong> are decorated in crisp whites with luxury furnishings, terracotta floors and views over the sea from the balcony. They measure 16-23m² and include air conditioning, TV, minibar and free wifi. They can sleep up to two adults.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Sea View Rooms</strong> measure 18-30m² and have a large balcony. They can sleep up to three adults.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> can accommodate up to three adults and measure 40m² with a sea view window and seating area.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> have a large bedroom and a separate living room with windows overlooking the sea. They measure 31-34m².</p>]]></roomsDescription>
